<p>I've searched a bit more and found that <code>rustyline::Editor</code> has got <a href="https://docs.rs/rustyline/17.0.1/rustyline/struct.Editor.html#method.set_helper" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><code>set_helper</code></a>/<a href="https://docs.rs/rustyline/17.0.1/rustyline/struct.Editor.html#method.helper_mut" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><code>helper_mut</code></a>/<a href="https://docs.rs/rustyline/17.0.1/rustyline/struct.Editor.html#method.helper" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><code>helper</code></a>; <code>set_helper</code> seem to be what I'm looking for, because the doc reads</p>
