<p>but I'm not sure what to do to achieve that. I'd have expected <code>set_helper</code> to accept a function that acceps a mutable reference to the state of the line and returns nothing, or something that would give equivalent &quot;power&quot;. But it takes a <code>()</code> instead.</p>
<p>How do I proceed? I've tried instatiating a compelter for filenames:</p>
