</code></pre>
<p>but passing it to <code>rl.set_helper(...)</code> (with or without <code>Some</code> around it) fails to typecheck because the method expects a <code>()</code>.</p>
<p>Indeed, this type-checks, expectedly, but it's obviously not doing anything:</p>
