/// This macro shows the safe pattern for generated code:
/// - call through a helper module where `Foo` is NOT in scope
/// - so `inst.go()` can only resolve to an inherent method
/// - if inherent `go` is missing, compilation fails (instead of runtime recursion)
macro_rules! impl_foo_by_inherent_go {
